2
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,990
=Episod 36=

3
00:02:27,510 --> 00:02:29,900
Jadi anda telah bersedia selama ini.

4
00:02:47,230 --> 00:02:48,070
Dia Simu!

5
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:49,460
Dia Simu!

6
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:52,980
Dia Simu,

7
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:54,420
