58
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:34,740
dengan Teknik Rahsia Chiling.

59
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:35,860
Kenapa Yan Ke boleh

60
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:37,030
kawal semangat boneka itu

61
00:05:37,030 --> 00:05:38,060
