146
00:09:55,350 --> 00:09:56,590
Moyang Besar.

147
00:10:01,190 --> 00:10:02,190
Perkara yang rumit?

148
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:05,470
Banyak roh jahat
telah muncul di Youzhou

149
00:10:05,470 --> 00:10:06,430
