161
00:10:26,780 --> 00:10:27,620
Di Dunia Fana,

162
00:10:27,990 --> 00:10:28,860
anda mesti berhati-hati.

163
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:30,540
Moyang Besar,

164
00:10:31,020 --> 00:10:32,430
